metadata.description:
The KlubList NFT collection opens the doors to the biggest clubs and festivals in the world. Owning one of the 7777 unique KlubList wristbands gives you the opportunity to win a lifetime access to Amnesia Ibiza, World Club Dome, Supersonic, We Are Fstvl, Rampage Open Air, Caprices Festival, Barcelona Beach Festival, Green Valley, LWE Events, Bootshaus and many other amazing perks. 

Limited to 777 soulbound passes, Mint Pass holders will be eligible to claim 2 x NFTs of The KlubList collection and will be rewarded with 777 KlubCoin tokens. 24 hours before the drop date, the addresses on Ethereum holding our Mint Pass NFTs will be automatically snapshot and be given mint rights to claim 2 x KlubList NFTs free of charge at the drop date (except gas fees) and their KlubCoin tokens will be airdropped.

Join our Discord : https://discord.gg/theklub 

Check the collection : https://klublist.clubbingtv.com/
